column3: Named Attribute Set for Query Parameter 'includefields' of QIDO-RS and WADO-RS Metadata or by Query Parameter 'comparefield' of DIFF-RS requests.
Unconstrained text description of this Attribute Set
Specifies if this Attribute Set is used by Query Parameter 'includefields' of QIDO-RS and WADO-RS Metadata or by Query Parameter 'comparefield' of DIFF-RS requests.
ID used by Query Parameter 'includefields' of QIDO-RS and WADO-RS Metadata requests and by Query Parameter 'comparefield' of DIFF-RS requests to refer this Attribute Set.
Number used to order Attribute Sets.
Boolean to indicate whether this Attribute Set is presently installed on the archive device
